author: Kevin McRae
title: Duke vs. Florida State: Live Score, Highlights and Reaction
text:
0 Comments 
No. 7 Duke visits No. 9 Florida State in a huge ACC matchup Tuesday night, and Bleacher Report will bring you all the live action from the Donald L. Tucker Civic Center in Tallahassee. 
The Blue Devils (14-2, 2-1 ACC ) will be without coach Mike Krzyzewski as he continues to recover from back surgery. His team responded well to his first absence from the sidelines with a 93-82 home win over Boston College on Saturday. 
Jayson Tatum led Duke with 22 points and six rebounds. 
The Seminoles (15-1, 3-0 ACC ) are one of the early season's biggest surprises and are a perfect 11-0 on their home court this season. But they can expect the challenge level to rise significantly with the Blue Devils coming to town. 
They enter this game with 11 straight wins including at No. 19 Virginia and home against Virginia Tech. 
Bleacher Report's live coverage is set to begin at 8 p.m. ET. 
You can watch live on ACC Network.
